data.description: Nine-foot ceilings on the first floor welcome you into this beautiful 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath townhouse with loft overlooking great room. This home is IMMACULATE and just like new! Open kitchen with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances, dining area and great room with electric fireplace and overlooking privacy fenced back patio. Maintenance free exterior with brick accents, upgraded beaded vinyl siding and vinyl wrapped trim, raised panel shutters and 30 year architectural shingles. Raised panel insulated garage door and owner installed shelving for storage or workshop. Backyard is private with vinyl stockade privacy fencing. Make this Town House your new Town Home!
